{"tid":2131301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際人權組織：香港國安法有如鎮壓藍圖","createTime":"2020-07-29T18:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T05:50:48.000Z","uid":141151,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ebda96cdb6c2d479d9bc8a8e9aab72b2b762c257","tid":2131301,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"國際人權組織：香港國安法有如鎮壓藍圖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/human-rights-watch-on-hk-ns-law-20200729/5521917.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fhuman-rights-watch-on-hk-ns-law-20200729%2F5521917.html&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=5a86dcdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/human-rights-watch-on-hk-ns-law-20200729/5521917.html</a><br />\n<br />\n總部位於紐約的國際人權組織&ldquo;人權觀察&rdquo;(Human Rights Watch)星期三表示，香港當局已經迅速開始依據新制定的《國家安全法》起訴和平言論、限制言論自由，對港人基本自由產生寒蟬效應。<br />\n<br />\n這部由中國政府於2020年6月30日起實施的法律，是北京自1997年主權移交以來對港人自由最猛烈的攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n該法許多條文還可能對香港人權保障造成毀滅性的長期影響，包括成立專責安全事務的秘密機關、剝奪公正審判的權利、賦予警隊更廣泛權力、加強管束公民社會與媒體以及削弱司法監督。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">人權觀察中國部資深研究員王松蓮表示：&ldquo;北京在一夕之間奪走了香港人的人權，長久對自由習以為常的香港人，現在只要持有或呼喊當局不喜歡的旗幟或口號，就可能被判處重刑。&rdquo;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n過去一個月，香港警方至少4次在民主示威中引用國安法，該法也正在迫使參政人士和團體改變其參與政治的方式和場所，還限制了88萬學童的受教權和信息、意見與自由表達。<br />\n<br />\n此外，政治審查也延伸到一般大眾自由獲得信息的權利，該法的寒蟬效益還擴及到商業界，並規定金融服務業者必須向當局報告可能違反該法的客戶資料。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><br />\n人權觀察中國部資深研究員王松蓮說：&ldquo;香港國安法無非是一份鎮壓藍圖，各國應該公開譴責，並為香港人提供避風港，拒絕配合該法在海外適用。&rdquo;</span></strong>"},{"pid":"12a3875cad9590878754785257a08be9048d0e81","tid":2131301,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66eeb8b11a0cfea6ffab3e1bd4e211b158167a20","tid":2131301,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T18:27:43.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"2499ebfd0271782320a5432c5dea18f2677e3905","tid":2131301,"uid":281189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T18:36:57.000Z","msg":"香港已經係一個大陸嘅普通城市<br />\n班中立撚返工撚繼續扮睇唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a755de7edb261c912620f3668f21e5b86007f9c","tid":2131301,"uid":53610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T19:01:11.000Z","msg":"加到光速，睇下邊個死先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1288465820109230088\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1288465820109230088&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=48f87c30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1288465820109230088&h=1c63b70c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1288465820109230088</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1288460598318161921?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1288460598318161921%3Fs%3D21&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=d1ada41c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1288460598318161921%3Fs%3D21&h=e1bfa4a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1288460598318161921?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JackHHazlewood/status/1288468716133416960?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJackHHazlewood%2Fstatus%2F1288468716133416960%3Fs%3D19&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=dbb4be59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJackHHazlewood%